<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪带着一个小桶来到体育馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她刚度假回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要把这些藏起来吗？” 她问邓恩老师，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在大家来之前？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师看了看满满一桶的贝壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪和邓恩老师走到操场上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把贝壳藏在秋千下面和球门后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还把一些贝壳藏在篮球架和树的附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他孩子们到的时候，他们刚好藏好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师向大家说明了今天的活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要寻宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不能告诉你们找的是什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们要怎么找呢？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我给你们一个提示。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们是来自海洋的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>找到五个后，就放到桌子上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 莉琪补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做很酷的东西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你们好运！” 邓恩老师挥手说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“提示一点儿用都没有。” 贾森抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有用。我知道我们要找的是什么。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经想到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，尼娜大喊：“我找到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男生们跑到尼娜那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在秋千旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心别踩到了！” 她大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们很容易碎的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是什么？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜伸出手。“是贝壳。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家知道了要找什么，所以贝壳很容易都被找到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，大家都回到了桌子旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们找到了贝壳。” 伊坦说，“现在呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪帮我们从沙滩捡来了这些贝壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她爸爸还在每个贝壳上打了孔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就让莉琪来说一说今天的手工吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪自豪地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做海风风铃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿起一个风铃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们家去年做了这个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有四个贝壳和一个海玻璃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个是漂木。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是漂木？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在海上漂了很久的木头。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也带了一些漂木给你们。” 莉琪补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 尼娜说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要怎么做风铃呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很简单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你只需要把所有东西都绑在漂木上就可以了。” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，我们要做挂钩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>剪一条大约六十厘米的细绳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把绳子的一端绑在漂木的一端。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把细绳的另一端绑在漂木的另一端。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，我们就可以挂贝壳了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>剪五条大约三十厘米的细绳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把绳子穿过贝壳上的孔，打个结。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把绳子的另一端绑在漂木上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有贝壳都用这种方法绑好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把贝壳摆好，剪绳子，开始做手工。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要把结打紧。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，谢谢。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这让我想起了加利福尼亚的海滩。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把一个粉红色的小贝壳绑在风铃上，然后笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天她把海边度假的快乐分享给了朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这种感觉就和海风一样清爽！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>